**Last Updated: March 6, 2025**

### Introduction

Welcome to Solatrack's Privacy Policy (hereinafter referred to as the "Bot"). We are committed to protecting the data collected through this Bot. This Policy explains what types of data we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your personal information when interacting with the Bot.

### Data We Collect

Solatrack collects the following data:

- Discord user ID
- Discord server ID
- Commands used and preferences
- Tracked Solana wallet addresses
- Custom configuration settings

We do not have access to:
- Text content of messages that don't mention the bot or aren't part of a command
- Your email address, billing information, or other Discord account details protected by Discord
- Private keys or recovery phrases of Solana wallets

### How We Use Your Data

The collected data is used for the following purposes:
- Enabling the Solana wallet tracking service
- Providing personalized performance analytics
- Facilitating copytrading features
- Improving the Bot's user experience
- Troubleshooting technical issues and maintenance

### Legal Basis for Processing

By using Solatrack, you consent to the collection and processing of your data as described in this policy. We only collect and use your personal data to provide you with proper access to the service.

### Data Retention

Data is retained for as long as necessary to provide the service or until you request its deletion. Data is stored in a secure environment with appropriate protection measures.

### Data Sharing

We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for commercial purposes. Your data may only be shared in the following cases:
- If required by law or judicial proceedings
- To protect our rights, property, or safety
- With your explicit consent

### Data Security

We take the security of your information very seriously and implement appropriate protection measures:
- Restricted access management
- Secure authentication
- Firewalls
- Regular security updates
- Access logging

### Your Rights

In accordance with applicable data protection laws, you have the following rights:
- Right to access your personal data
- Right to rectify inaccurate data
- Right to erasure of your data
- Right to withdraw consent
- Right to object to processing

To exercise these rights, you can contact us via the contact information provided below.

### Changes to This Policy

We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time. Changes take effect immediately upon posting. We encourage you to regularly review this policy to stay informed of updates.

### Contact Us

If you have any questions about this privacy policy or the use of your data, please contact us at: [Your email address].

By using Solatrack, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this privacy policy and agree to the collection and use of your information as described in this document.
